---
import { Code, Globe, Users, Lightbulb, Target, Award } from 'lucide-react';
---

<section id="about" class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-b from-gray-900 to-black">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">
        <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-400 to-pink-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
          About Me
        </span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        Passionate AI developer and visionary founder dedicated to creating technology that protects and empowers people worldwide
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 mb-16">
      <!-- Personal Story -->
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-900/50 to-black/50 border border-purple-500/20 rounded-2xl p-8">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4 flex items-center">
            <Lightbulb className="w-6 h-6 text-yellow-400 mr-3" />
            My Story
          </h3>
          <div class="space-y-4 text-gray-300">
            <p>
              I'm Loretta Chapman, an AI visionary and founder with a deep passion for using technology to save lives and protect people. 
              My journey began with a simple belief: artificial intelligence should serve humanity's greatest needs.
            </p>
            <p>
              What started as curiosity about AI's potential has evolved into a mission-driven career focused on developing 
              life-saving technologies. From emergency rescue systems to global safety platforms, I build AI solutions 
              that make a real difference in crisis situations.
            </p>
            <p>
              Every project I create is guided by one question: "How can this technology protect and empower people?" 
              This philosophy drives everything from my humanitarian AI platforms to innovative business solutions.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Skills & Expertise -->
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-900/50 to-black/50 border border-purple-500/20 rounded-2xl p-8">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6 flex items-center">
            <Code className="w-6 h-6 text-blue-400 mr-3" />
            Expertise
          </h3>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
            <div class="space-y-3">
              <div class="flex items-center space-x-2">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-purple-400 rounded-full"></div>
                <span class="text-gray-300">AI/Machine Learning</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center space-x-2">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-pink-400 rounded-full"></div>
                <span class="text-gray-300">Emergency Response Systems</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center space-x-2">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-blue-400 rounded-full"></div>
                <span class="text-gray-300">Global Safety Platforms</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center space-x-2">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-green-400 rounded-full"></div>
                <span class="text-gray-300">Humanitarian Technology</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-3">
              <div class="flex items-center space-x-2">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-yellow-400 rounded-full"></div>
                <span class="text-gray-300">Full-Stack Development</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center space-x-2">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-red-400 rounded-full"></div>
                <span class="text-gray-300">Business Innovation</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center space-x-2">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-indigo-400 rounded-full"></div>
                <span class="text-gray-300">Product Strategy</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center space-x-2">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-orange-400 rounded-full"></div>
                <span class="text-gray-300">Crisis Management Tech</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Values & Approach -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-16">
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-500 to-pink-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
          <Target className="w-8 h-8 text-white" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Purpose-Driven</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-300">Every technology I build serves a greater purpose - protecting lives and empowering communities</p>
      </div>

      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 to-purple-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
          <Globe className="w-8 h-8 text-white" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Global Impact</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-300">Thinking beyond borders to create solutions that can help people anywhere in the world</p>
      </div>

      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-r from-green-500 to-blue-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
          <Users className="w-8 h-8 text-white" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Human-Centered</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-300">Technology should serve people, not the other way around - every solution puts humans first</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Current Focus -->
    <div class="text-center">
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-900/50 to-black/50 border border-purple-500/20 rounded-2xl p-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
          <Award className="w-6 h-6 text-gold-400 mr-3" />
          Current Focus
        </h3>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
          I'm currently developing advanced AI systems for emergency response and global safety coordination. 
          My flagship project, <strong class="text-purple-400">Peacekeeper</strong>, is an open-source platform that helps communities 
          detect risks, improve crisis coordination, and protect people in emergency situations. 
          <br><br>
          <span class="text-pink-400 italic">
            "What happens when you fund a quirky AI visionary? ü§∑‚Äç‚ôÇÔ∏è Only one way to find out..."
          </span>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>